  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is conducted in Africa and Asia. The aim of this study is to evaluate the
      efficacy, safety and convenience of using repaglinide (NovoNorm®) in type 2 diabetes
      management in routine clinical practice.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
